desc.en: Ningbo Rail Transit is an urban rail transit system serving Ningbo City, Zhejiang Province, China. As of January 2023, Ningbo Rail Transit has 5 operating lines, namely Line 1, Line 2, Line 3, Line 4 and Line 5, with a total operating mileage of about 185 kilometers and 127 stations.
